branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VXZ series for air is a 2 port, pilot operated solenoid valve capable of operating at higher differential pressures by maintaining a zero differential pressure on the seat. Available with resin, aluminum, brass or stainless steel body material. Standard NBR seal and optional FKM for use with ozone resistant applications. Available in port size 1/4 to 1 inch. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 1.7 to 9.4.
&lt;/p&gt;

