&lt;li&gt;Maximum pressure: 1.5 MPa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IP65 enclosure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valve type: normally closed, and normally open&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VXZ series for water is a 2 port, pilot operated solenoid valve capable of operating at higher differential pressures by maintaining a zero differential pressure on the seat. The molded coil offers low power consumption, long life and high reliability. Standard NBR seal and optional FKM seal for use with deionized water. Available for port sizes ranging from 1/4 to 1 inch. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 1.9 to 10.2.
&lt;/p&gt;

